    "Overall, the problem can be solved as a semi-definite problem, that can be solved in a run-time with low-order polynomial effort with interior point methods.",
    "Duality theory readily provides a rigorous certificate for the solution 93.In the proof, we refrain from explicitly specifying the definition of σ in relation to the original states ρ 1, …, ρ N. Indeed, the success criterion is that the resulting matrix Ŵ is well-conditioned.",
